<![CDATA[<font face="arial" size="3">Hello {!Account.FirstName},</font><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">We hope you've been enjoying your time on the water so far! &nbsp;We want to make sure that you are completely, 100% satisfied with your new boat and that you will enjoy it for years to come. &nbsp;To ensure that everything is exactly the way you want it, I would like to invite you to come back in for a Multi-Point Courtesy Inspection!</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">We find that all too often, boat owners are willing to live with a slight inconvenience on their boat, when really it just requires the simplest tweak on our end. &nbsp;When you come in, please tell us everything! Any concerns you may have, anything that you are unsure of, anything that you require further training with, Anything! &nbsp;In return, we will look over your boat package and ensure that everything is where it should be and working correctly.&nbsp;</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Your lifelong boating happiness is paramount to us and like any vehicle, regular boat inspections and maintenance help keep you on the water and out of the Shop!</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">To schedule your Multi Point Courtesy Inspection:&nbsp;</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Please call us at the Service Desk at 1 (800) 459-8448 or&nbsp;</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Email Legend Customer Care at barrieservice@legendboats.com.</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Please be sure to let us know of any additional Services you would like completed while your boat is left with us.&nbsp;</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">We look forward to hearing from you. &nbsp;Have a Legendary day!</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div><font face="arial">{!User.Name}</font></div><div><font face="arial">{!User.Title}</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div>]]></td>
